text: Alectryon repandodentatus is a species of plant in the family Sapindaceae. It is found in Australia and Papua New Guinea. ==References== ==External links== * repandodentatus Category:Sapindales of Australia Category:Flora of Papua New Guinea Category:Vulnerable flora of Australia Category:Nature Conservation Act endangered biota Category:Vulnerable biota of Queensland Category:Endangered flora of Australia Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
